casebody.data:
ANIMAL CARE TRUST, et al., petitioners,
v.
UNITED PET SUPPLY INC. No. 14-954. Supreme Court of the United States June 1, 2015.

Opinion

Motion of International Municipal Lawyers Association, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Motion of American Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Animals for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.
